channel.title: Getting my server online
channel.description: Ok guys, I have tried everything and then some to get my server online. I am all out of ideas. I can say that I've been to at least 5 different websites dealing with how to portforward, or how to use utorrent, or just about anything dealing with making a server. I've made my server, I've got my No-Ip Ip account. I've portforwarded correctly (I think. I could be wrong, I would take a screen shot of it, but I don't know how.) I've checked "canyouseeme.org" and it can't see me. I've watched hundereds of youtube videos, if someone could help me get it working, you might as well be my hero haha.
